{"tid":142202,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真救教］扑嘢成日扑到一半 會軟左","createTime":"2017-03-03T14:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T14:13:39.000Z","uid":27837,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6b8a905835e600be690cb6e8008e3b3718b99e","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"各位巴打細佬今年23歲<br />\n同女朋友一齊已經五個月<br />\n同佢有搞嘢已經四個幾月，大概一星期一到兩次<br />\n我係同佢先破處<br />\n呢幾個月搞嘢一直都唔順利<br />\n開始發覺自己係唔係性功能有問題<br />\n發覺自己每次仆嘢仆到5到10分鐘到就會軟<br />\n之後有等下就會硬返，有時軟咗就停左唔搞<br />\n另外有時戴套就會軟<br />\n<br />\n係唔係以前打得飛機太多習慣咗隻手嘅感覺？<br />\n中二開始打飛機，高form開始幾乎日日一次到依家20幾歲，<br />\n有時覺得仆野係冇手咁舒服咁緊<br />\n仆緊嘅時候就會覺得冇乜感覺加上郁得攰就會開始軟<br />\n發覺呢個問題之後我都開始戒丁<br />\n依家幾乎一星期一次<br />\n 唔知係唔係心理因素壓力搞到我依家有時打丁都扯唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我去睇過一兩次呢方面嘅醫生，佢哋話我太緊張之類<br />\n我成日都型住型住扑嘢會唔會軟<br />\n成日問自己會唔會扯唔起<br />\n我又唔係因為扑嘢面紅心跳果種緊張而係成日有以上呢種焦慮但心<br />\n<br />\n 我出咗咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 有冇巴打曾經都試過咁樣，係唔係真係打得飛機太多，20幾歲已經陽萎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我巴打有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6831506c97fc28fb3a73c2c9e287cc572c902ea9","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"補多少少資料<br />\n我幾鍾意健身，有keep住一個星期健三四日<br />\n應該唔係運動方面有問題掛？<br />\n另外我有飲蛋白粉一星期飲兩三次， 都係健完身先會飲，會唔會係飲得太多嘅問題？"},{"pid":"6462ad14b663041e1f91de0b40a6545303f091b6","tid":142202,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"試下同男人扑野"},{"pid":"6857d4cc4b498fb1e3665469d6b2ae298042fa60","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下同男人扑野</blockquote><br />\n絲打認真求教唔好玩我啦"},{"pid":"3c2820cc4adbdada8a6fa3df020fb4b11454eaf0","tid":142202,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"你唔夠咸濕姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dba26ba4ca3a037350849da9109bc070df3e7d","tid":142202,"uid":10698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"你條女係唔係冇波？"},{"pid":"042844600a1f212954b382463ca901ad263f522e","tid":142202,"uid":68701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"無快感  唔夠刺激 唔戴套會改善"},{"pid":"97adc5d3f96b2f9f5dc7261278418fe8c62ef0b0","tid":142202,"uid":86352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:27:57.000Z","msg":"打少d丁<br />\n前戲做足d，咁條女入戲d肉緊d，你都會舒服d<br />\n有時龜頭唔夠敏感既話，個套唔好太厚，唔係乜閪都feel唔到<br />\n亦都可能係姿勢問題<br />\n有時有d體位係唔岩feel<br />\n轉下pose，講下咸濕野，大家投入d都會有幫助<br />\n總之唔好諗太多，有得屌個時就輕鬆d享受下"},{"pid":"8c17d37b98f5c24faa05ae214f751a8932e3f626","tid":142202,"u