:35:45.000Z","msg":"條女話自己係處，但第一次博佢冇流血<br />\n但真係入左幾次先入到<br />\n關於晨勃方面，好似冇日日都晨勃，兩至三日一次晨勃，係唔係收得皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69112c984c7c48f209f5ea92357a51e72496835","tid":142202,"uid":25688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"食藥啦，幫到你"},{"pid":"f50252e171d7273d65d61f17d6ed5aa5ecbc535d","tid":142202,"uid":25688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"犀利士"},{"pid":"5839cbf4287560cb242b0e1c4574d00399984214","tid":142202,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"巴打話俾你知好多人都係咁，但十個有九個都係心理問題。我就唔信打飛機會攪到咁。<br />\n我個case係戴套即軟，屌到中途就軟。但第三第四次扑已經無哂事。<br />\n會唔會係環境問題？你同佢屌時，佢屋企人係度？你緊張驚被人聽到，係會軟。<br />\n同埋搵個好既體位，搵個你一定會屌到射既位置。"},{"pid":"7c8bd6f71132dc36e5af5bb0320eb1c8524a8291","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>犀利士</blockquote><br />\n食過一次半粒，好似好少少，但之後好似變返平時咁，冇理由20幾歲次次都食嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fea193eca5d3467f12965567eef775bcae5f3e","tid":142202,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女話自己係處，但第一次博佢冇流血<br />\n但真係入左幾次先入到<br />\n關於晨勃方面，好似冇日日都晨勃，兩至三日一次晨勃，係唔係收得皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇反應啦 有無嗌晒救命話好痛先"},{"pid":"247ba7acd7445cafc6d9871e8f4f7d1df1acfdd8","tid":142202,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>犀利士</blockquote><br />\n食過一次半粒，好似好少少，但之後好似變返平時咁，冇理由20幾歲次次都食嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食多幾次慢慢減藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965013ec006fe1cd8240d17950249253eb794c08","tid":142202,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:39:21.000Z","msg":"仲有軟左 即刻停 唔攪<br />\n咁點解唔用手/玩具 攪到佢高潮？<br />\n我覺得你驚自己軟，滿足唔到佢，都係個潛在壓力"},{"pid":"ffe6cfa054d652dd4778454275933d0818d9d585","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打話俾你知好多人都係咁，但十個有九個都係心理問題。我就唔信打飛機會攪到咁。<br />\n我個case係戴套即軟，屌到中途就軟。但第三第四次扑已經無哂事。<br />\n會唔會係環境問題？你同佢屌時，佢屋企人係度？你緊張驚被人聽到，係會軟。<br />\n同埋搵個好既體位，搵個你一定會屌到射既位置。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係好多人都會咁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 為我之前都係青頭仔唔係好知呢啲嘢<br />\n有時係會驚啲roommate返嚟會聽到好尷尬<br />\n（同其他大學fd租屋）<br />\n唔可以解答多少少有咩改善方法<br />\n麻煩曬巴打"},{"pid":"a43952e39eb9639a77d268f61ffae23bc8d06a48","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條女話自己係處，但第一次博佢冇流血<br />\n但真係入左幾次先入到<br />\n關於晨勃方面，好似冇日日都晨勃，兩至三日一次晨勃，係唔係收得皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇反應啦 有無嗌晒救命話好痛先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見佢幾痛下， feel到好似真係冇呃我"},{"pid":"9a19ea142e2630e71ec8356d6da1be6b02a7226d","tid":142202,"uid":57217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"計1000-7"},{"pid":"6bd05399ef1d3a43bd1abe730a57f553a7383c5a","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打話俾你知好多人都係咁，但十個有九個都係心理問題。我就唔信打飛機會攪到咁。<br />\n我個case係戴套即軟，屌到中途就軟。但第三第四次扑已經無哂事。<br />\n會唔會係環境問題？你同佢屌時，佢屋企人係度？你緊張驚被人聽到，係會軟。<br />\n同埋搵個好既體位，搵個你一定會屌到射既位置。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外巴打你今年幾多歲"},{"pid":"a64282a1429a4bc3d9e7ba7f84478d922996f089","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計1000-7</blockquote><br />\n？"},{"pid":"91f0d2986039310d9c36035a4d9f68b7684054d7","tid":142202,"uid":12359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打話俾你知好多人都係咁，但十個有九個都係心理問題。我就唔信打飛機會攪到咁。<br />\n我個case係戴套即軟，屌到中途就軟。但第三第四次扑已經無哂事。<br />\n會唔會係環境問題？你同佢屌時，佢屋企人係度？你緊張驚被人聽到，係會軟。<br />\n同埋搵個好既體位，搵個你一定會屌到射既位置。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外巴打你今年幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n我依排都係咁 唔知係咪打得J多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f7a08a0118f300ec02595f305059fc81a9ee7d","tid":142202,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"唔好用持久裝安全套"},{"pid":"b6f662b794fc81485e071bc1d1cc06c55fde513d","tid":142202,"uid":52053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔好做gym啦"},{"pid":"f7f10ca7c49defbf066b484414d6d3fecd4adb34","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打話俾你知好多人都係咁，但十個有九個都係心理問題。我就唔信打飛機會攪到咁。<br />\n我個case係戴套即軟，屌到中途就軟。但第三第四次扑已經無哂事。<br />\n會唔會係環境問題？你同佢屌時，佢屋企人係度？你緊張驚被人聽到，係會軟。<br />\n同埋搵個好既體位，搵個你一定會屌到射既位置。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外巴打你今年幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n愛想問其實仆野幾耐先係正常時間，我指係插入去到射，我有時會驚自己時間短，所以次次事前都會睇吓時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcf9e2b4aeebded466899291297fc3c06ab4a32","tid":142202,"uid":52053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"試下飲下啲補酒"},{"pid":"529583e5d04fc7c0f69fd7312566a3212cae0c27","tid":142202,"uid":5372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"認真...<br />\n我同條女扑左10年先有你果d 徵狀<br />\n不過呢十年一直keep住帶套<br />\n最近佢去左打針,可以唔賽套瘋狂中出<br />\n之後扑野就好撚正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688b5a1853a46f7546fcf0258f233b7989c63d26","tid":142202,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"累都會<br />\n<br />\n好似你長跑咁，有時太爽你未到終點就爆100米既速度，好易搞到冇氣，餘下既時間就朵皮<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好咁早太激動<br />\n<br />\n另外前戲個啲巴打有講"},{"pid":"206b006b7f44d778df61c7eef9fa7f1bc2cfdcaf","tid":142202,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打話俾你知好多人都係咁，但十個有九個都係心理問題。我就唔信打飛機會攪到咁。<br />\n我個case係戴套即軟，屌到中途就軟。但第三第四次扑已經無哂事。<br />\n會唔會係環境問題？你同佢屌時，佢屋企人係度？你緊張驚被人聽到，係會軟。<br />\n同埋搵個好既體位，搵個你一定會屌到射既位置。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係好多人都會咁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 為我之前都係青頭仔唔係好知呢啲嘢<br />\n有時係會驚啲roommate返嚟會聽到好尷尬<br />\n（同其他大學fd租屋）<br />\n唔可以解答多少少有咩改善方法<br />\n麻煩曬巴打</blockquote><br />\n我有幾個朋友都試過上套即軟<br />\n你試下搵一次完全無壓力、無外界影響之下扑，例如租酒店。<br />\n我同條女第一次，係佢屋企，我覺得個地方唔熟，令我表現差左。<br />\n仲有 ，我用0.03時上套好難，好難套個dom落根部。但橙色杜記就一野套到。我覺得上套太慢都會即軟。<br />\n其實都係同女人傾下，可能叫佢見你軟時含下你。"},{"pid":"fb7eb9a9a78e1e8d04c2f6a78de1517b62ea39af","tid":142202,"uid":8496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打細佬今年23歲<br />\n同女朋友一齊已經五個月<br />\n同佢有搞嘢已經四個幾月，大概一星期一到兩次<br />\n我係同佢先破處<br />\n呢幾個月搞嘢一直都唔順利<br />\n開始發覺自己係唔係性功能有問題<br />\n發覺自己每次仆嘢仆到5到10分鐘到就會軟<br />\n之後有等下就會硬返，有時軟咗就停左唔搞<br />\n另外有時戴套就會軟<br />\n<br />\n係唔係以前打得飛機太多習慣咗隻手嘅感覺？<br />\n中二開始打飛機，高form開始幾乎日日一次到依家20幾歲，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有時覺得仆野係冇手咁舒服咁緊</span><br />\n仆緊嘅時候就會覺得冇乜感覺加上郁得攰就會開始軟<br />\n發覺呢個問題之後我都開始戒丁<br />\n依家幾乎一星期一次<br />\n 唔知係唔係心理因素壓力搞到我依家有時打丁都扯唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我去睇過一兩次呢方面嘅醫生，佢哋話我太緊張之類<br />\n我成日都型住型住扑嘢會唔會軟<br />\n成日問自己會唔會扯唔起<br />\n我又唔係因為扑嘢面紅心跳果種緊張而係成日有以上呢種焦慮但心<br />\n<br />\n 我出咗咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 有冇巴打曾經都試過咁樣，係唔係真係打得飛機太多，20幾歲已經陽萎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我巴打有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 你條女肯定唔係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 你會唔會唔夠投入？<br />\n<br />\n3. 究竟你係想講扑野定仆野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">叫你條女幫你含幾下先啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"85ba9262d0e3e0377552ecd723cd7333fe6af0ee","tid":142202,"uid":57217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>計1000-7</blockquote><br />\n？</blockquote><br />\n不斷減，啪緊果陣計，分散注意力"},{"pid":"c2a66bba2dcdb746072c2914c5b28cc65dc5edcb","tid":142202,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>犀利士</blockquote><br />\n有冇食評？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff8532610042f097061f518515f56654331f40d","tid":142202,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計1000-7</blockquote><br />\n東京喰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65821dc18959a0479649c2b9ed52af1716428908","tid":142202,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打話俾你知好多人都係咁，但十個有九個都係心理問題。我就唔信打飛機會攪到咁。<br />\n我個case係戴套即軟，屌到中途就軟。但第三第四次扑已經無哂事。<br />\n會唔會係環境問題？你同佢屌時，佢屋企人係度？你緊張驚被人聽到，係會軟。<br />\n同埋搵個好既體位，搵個你一定會屌到射既位置。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外巴打你今年幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n愛想問其實仆野幾耐先係正常時間，我指係插入去到射，我有時會驚自己時間短，所以次次事前都會睇吓時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n22咋，但呢個女朋友唔係第一次。<br />\n可能第一次極認真拍拖，驚滿足唔到佢，頭幾次好軟。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇時間啦...你仲緊張...你秒射左咪用手囉...<br />\n睇過有個訪問，問av女優 男人點先學到滿足女人，佢叫男人睇女同片..人地玩手指玩到"},{"pid":"7f13b2dcf368cdd4d0345fc4e7843d56f59e18e0","tid":142202,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬆咗啲啫 唔係你問題"},{"pid":"b3c3df1fd934f4fe5a9d83e52c3fe4fd0d08549d","tid":142202,"uid":33595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係帶套即軟，唔帶會唔夠硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實初初冇咩野，我可能之前有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bef42d9bc56006900a36c95c88b34f25268fab","tid":142202,"uid":18616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"🍊"},{"pid":"32ab255e8505d0cf68a1496713f3900a783f7bb8","tid":142202,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81eb4a05f51126c1a30d40aa52cc984acb6b456e","tid":142202,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2a40f6aac65d8ebbff68cab8c1b0c126b5b2246","tid":142202,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"認真, 陽痿<br />\n搵蕭別離幫手"},{"pid":"dceb60f82995899db6c915944e9fc1a81c4e8b28","tid":142202,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b666aa253720ac827685623ecd3f74ba9095aaf","tid":142202,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9118f45619444dc2651143fc5811d0df7c5cc9b4","tid":142202,"uid":44179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"認真答，你唔夠愛佢"},{"pid":"75b1abf4fb8e5d716b0ce45812d32ecd3f6815ab","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:02:57.000Z","msg":"前叫過一兩次雞，緊張得滯幾乎完全冇扯過"},{"pid":"249b71ff9f8dd8ac8c71e58fcd4958a45163be22","tid":142202,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勃起功能障礙又稱陽痿。陰莖勃起硬度不足以性交或不能維持至射精。美國曾在普通人群中調查，其發病率在成年男性中佔8%；中國曾估計約佔10%。</blockquote><br />\n咁要維持到幾耐先正常<br />\n我帶套都好易軟 但唔帶未試過軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bc0e4c83f427f12d5d95b0381659445cd881b2","tid":142202,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"你咁樣已經係老末期，只有求燈神蕭生燈一燈，即刻變返巨龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b4627f0f650fd09d00c7bee684a44faa21ba7d","tid":142202,"uid":23329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"割左包皮未"},{"pid":"fc92da0344f6c3091aef6ba424371d9d417dc2ca","tid":142202,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"原來咁多巴打都會 以為得自己試過戴套軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febc60afe31b0b1c37dfefb3fd350e92d570d91a","tid":142202,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>割左包皮未</blockquote><br />\n冇"},{"pid":"509926e967ff9dc397340554ec4e182b0e7b9d60","tid":142202,"uid":38583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"巴打試下同條女傾下完多d其他嘢例如角色扮演"},{"pid":"53eb520714d0296bc6c48370ef29a9ff84283565","tid":142202,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"教你 你下次想扑野 開post叫巴打黎 你係隔離睇住打飛機 你又爽 巴打又爽"},{"pid":"7be977f5d03b36b08040404cab8d835c4e3a2306","tid":142202,"uid":85765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T