-03T16:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打咁多丁腎虧咪軟囉，<br />\n戒色先幫到你喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我前個日打左J 第二日多數都好難硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d259b4d6300b9a34926d6ca376f041a9ef5290","tid":142202,"uid":25688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:11:32.000Z","msg":"其實心理問題影響多，心理質素、壓力影響勃起硬度同時間，食藥其實幫到你，食一個週期，起碼你個一年半載一定射完都硬住出。<br />\n<br />\n不過食藥係改善唔到你個心理壓力問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d532fbffa41119f5a48b2bba37f13d21fec3930b","tid":142202,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打細佬今年23歲<br />\n同女朋友一齊已經五個月<br />\n同佢有搞嘢已經四個幾月，大概一星期一到兩次<br />\n我係同佢先破處<br />\n呢幾個月搞嘢一直都唔順利<br />\n開始發覺自己係唔係性功能有問題<br />\n發覺自己每次仆嘢仆到5到10分鐘到就會軟<br />\n之後有等下就會硬返，有時軟咗就停左唔搞<br />\n另外有時戴套就會軟<br />\n<br />\n係唔係以前打得飛機太多習慣咗隻手嘅感覺？<br />\n中二開始打飛機，高form開始幾乎日日一次到依家20幾歲，<br />\n有時覺得仆野係冇手咁舒服咁緊<br />\n仆緊嘅時候就會覺得冇乜感覺加上郁得攰就會開始軟<br />\n發覺呢個問題之後我都開始戒丁<br />\n依家幾乎一星期一次<br />\n 唔知係唔係心理因素壓力搞到我依家有時打丁都扯唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我去睇過一兩次呢方面嘅醫生，佢哋話我太緊張之類<br />\n我成日都型住型住扑嘢會唔會軟<br />\n成日問自己會唔會扯唔起<br />\n我又唔係因為扑嘢面紅心跳果種緊張而係成日有以上呢種焦慮但心<br />\n<br />\n 我出咗咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 有冇巴打曾經都試過咁樣，係唔係真係打得飛機太多，20幾歲已經陽萎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我巴打有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對係心理 我以前都會 再加上驚佢軟就想快d射"},{"pid":"5e200ce9e54c944f364d81e7a2a88ae2bff9a6d5","tid":142202,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補多少少資料<br />\n我幾鍾意健身，有keep住一個星期健三四日<br />\n應該唔係運動方面有問題掛？<br />\n另外我有飲蛋白粉一星期飲兩三次， 都係健完身先會飲，會唔會係飲得太多嘅問題？</blockquote><br />\nav男優都會軟左<br />\n加上你睇av直接飛去扑野個part 令致個人對同條女扑野無咁多刺激度 建議一個禮拜打一次飛機 同埋少d睇av 現實搞野實無av咁癲"},{"pid":"a7e7fce99d4e3ed6cbeeda77540e6927361f40df","tid":142202,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"試下唔帶套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c7c29cc46616f262680ccdcb6dd0960cca6004","tid":142202,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"傳聞話試下扑野果陣心算，就持久d"},{"pid":"2d8aa886ad8621c3c9e18fd8769ecf182aad0ae0","tid":142202,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:31:38.000Z","msg":"早洩陽痿只不過係腎氣不足所致<br />\n臂氣不足，所以身體比警告你，唔好再射精，禁慾一年等身體恢復再節制扑野啦"},{"pid":"f8efa788d391e3fc0a9850beb94a31a4a2ff4811","tid":142202,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真, 陽痿<br />\n搵蕭別離幫手</blockquote><br />\n呢D案例見得太多